import React, { useState, useEffect } from 'react'; import { Box, AppBar, Toolbar, Typography, Button, Card, CardContent, Table, TableBody, TableCell, TableContainer, TableHead, TableRow, Paper, Container, Avatar, Grid, Chip } from '@mui/material'; import { ArrowBack, Add, Person, History, Email, Phone, Business, Delete, SwapHoriz, Edit } from '@mui/icons-material'; import kilowattImage from '../../assets/image.png'; import NavBar from '../shared/NavBar'; const ManagerDetail = ({ managerId, onNavigate, onLogout }) => { const [manager, setManager] = useState(null); const [associatedAccounts, setAssociatedAccounts] = useState([]); useEffect(() => { // Mock manager data const mockManager = { id: managerId, name: 'Sarah Johnson', title: 'Manager', email: 'sarah.johnson@propmanage.com', phone: '(713) 555-0123', managementCompany: 'Property Management Inc.', accountCount: 24, totalCommission: 125000, pendingContracts: 3, activeAccounts: 48 }; const mockAccounts = [ { id: 1, name: 'ABC Corporation', status: 'Active', contractEndDate: '12/31/2024', rate: '$0.085', monthlyCommission: '$1,500' }, // Add more accounts ]; setManager(mockManager); setAssociatedAccounts(mockAccounts); }, [managerId]); if (!manager) return null; return ( {}} /> {manager.name} {manager.title} {manager.email} {manager.phone} {manager.managementCompany} {manager.accountCount} Active Accounts {manager.activeAccounts} Total Billing ${manager.totalCommission.toLocaleString()} YTD Commission {manager.pendingContracts} Pending Contracts Associated Accounts Account Name Status Contract End Date Rate Monthly Commission {associatedAccounts.map((account) => ( {account.name} {account.contractEndDate} {account.rate} {account.monthlyCommission} ))}
); }; export default ManagerDetail;
